004package mkt;
005
006import java.util.ArrayList;
007import kut.Js;
008import kut.Arr;
009
010/** Result of 'Strategy.xxxSimple'. */
011public class StSimpleRs {
012  /** Number of sales. */
013  public final int sales;
014  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with closes. */
015  public final double assets;
016  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with prices. */
017  public final double accs;
018  /** Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with references. */
019  public final double rfAssets;
020
021  /**
022   * Constructor.
023   * @param sales Number of sales.
024   * @param assets Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with closes.
025   * @param accs Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with prices.
026   * @param rfAssets Cash + withdrawals + portfolio evaluated with references.
027   */
028  public StSimpleRs (int sales, double assets, double accs, double rfAssets) {
029    this.sales = sales;
030    this.assets = assets;
031    this.accs = accs;
032    this.rfAssets = rfAssets;
033  }
034
035  /**
036   * Returns object JSONized.
037   * @param o Ditto.
038   * @return Ditto.
039   */
040  public static String toJs (StSimpleRs o) {
041    return Js.w(Arr.mk(
042      Js.w(o.sales),
043      Js.w(o.assets),
044      Js.w(o.accs),
045      Js.w(o.rfAssets)
046    ));
047  }
048
049  /**
050   * Returns object from JSON.
051   * @param js JSON string.
052   * @return Ditto.
053   */
054  public static StSimpleRs fromJs (String js) {
055    ArrayList<String> a = Js.ra(js);
056    return new StSimpleRs(
057      (int)Js.rn(a.get(0)),
058      Js.rn(a.get(1)),
059      Js.rn(a.get(2)),
060      Js.rn(a.get(3))
061    );
062  }
063}
